Dialogs.Dialog: Oh, hello. Can you talk to me now?
Well, it's today... I'm making dinner, so why don't you eat with me at my house?
I have something to do today...
Was good. If so, I'm going back and preparing today, so come later?
really? It was good ♪ Then I'll prepare and wait, so I'll see you later.
Oh, I'm looking forward to it.
I have something to do today...
That's right... I'm sorry, but it's the next opportunity.
Come to think of it, isn't it the first time for me to eat at my house?
That's right. Somehow... don't get excited.
Well, I want you to eat the food I learned recently... I'll do it ♪
I'm thinking about the menu, but if there is a request, will it be accepted?
so? If so... I have a dish I learned recently, so I'll do it.
okay? Then, think about what you like and make it.
Yes, please wait. It's a self-confident work, so please look forward to it ♪
Please wait. Is it so good this time?
I'm sorry to have kept you waiting. I may have failed a little...
I tried something new. How about?
Today's food has my own arrangement. It's a bit different from the others ♪
Hey, do you know that I'm adding a little self-styled arrangement?
I arranged this a little. The recipe is fine, but I want to bring out my personality.
Today's cooking is a little extra work ♪
I hope you like my style of arranged dishes.
I wonder if Japanese food is as confident as anyone at school ♪
I'm good at seasoning Japanese food. I'm sure it's delicious, right?
I'd say it myself, but... are you pretty good at making Western food?
Maybe I can open a Western-style restaurant? n/a
If you eat the Western food I made, you won't be able to eat anything else ♪
I'm confident in Chinese food. I hope you can say it's delicious.
I'm confident in seasoning Chinese food. Do you have a lot of techniques?
Leave it to me for Chinese food ♪
I'm good at this type of food. You'll do it, right? n/a.
Recently, I like to cook this kind of food. I'm sure it's delicious?
After studying a lot, I've become good at cooking like this. How?
You can leave it to us for any dish ♪ I am confident that you will say it is delicious ▼
Nowadays I can make anything. Isn't it amazing?
How? It ’s nice to have a girlfriend who can make anything ▼
Japanese food is just a little different, and it's totally useless... How about?
When I make Japanese food, I try to be very polite, but... it's quite difficult.
I want to make your favorite Japanese food... but it doesn't go well. But I tried my best so why not try it?
Where is the point of seasoning Western food? Please tell me if you are not satisfied.
I'm not really good at making Western food... But I wanted to make you happy, so I made it so hard, right?
Western food seems easy, but why is it so difficult? I wonder if I can cover it with love...
Chinese food is really difficult... I'm trying to get closer to your taste...
How can the taste of Chinese food be decided? I tried my best to make it, but I'm sorry if it doesn't fit my taste?
I made it so hard... Is it okay? I'm not good at making Chinese food.
I wonder if I'm not suitable for this kind of cooking? Because I have a lot of love... I'm glad if you eat it.
I did my best, but... Isn't this right for you? I have to practice this type of cooking more …….
I still can't cook this kind of food well... But I did my best, so I hope you can eat it.
Recently, the food looks like a slump... I thought it would be a little better if I loved it... how about?
Somehow, the seasoning isn't decided exactly... Can you still eat it?
I can't make something that I can put out with confidence... Will you eat
Hey, it's the matching tableware you got. I finally used it ▼
I like the tableware you gave me. I wonder if two of them are lined up...
Hmm, thank you for your feast.
(When I ate homemade food, I got stronger. There seems to be something good!)
Hey, how was my rice? I think it was a good result.
How was the rice I made? You can answer honestly ▼
Hey, what was your impression of eating my home cooking? I only hear compliments …… Nante ♪
By the way... Then, would you like to hear your impressions of the food?
Hey, my home cooking... did it fit your taste?
How was it? ‥ …… I'm not as confident as I hear it.
I'm sorry... Today's food wasn't good, right?
I'm sorry... I wanted to make it properly.
After all? I thought you could say that ▼
Eh !? It would be nice if you were honest.
so? I was wondering if it would make me more happy, but... I hope it was delicious.
Well, I think it was delicious.
I see, thank you. Was good.
really? That's right... it was okay.
Is it a little different from your taste?
Eh... is that so? I thought I was able to do it well, but... I'll do my best again.
It's not my taste... I think it's a little different.
is that so……. You have to study your taste more.
Certainly... I wonder if it's different from my taste.
right……. But this time I'll do my best to get closer to my taste.
Hey, it's lunch... Sometimes it's better not to have a lunch box?
The dining room is also good
What are you saying, lunch is the best.
really? Then I will make it without hesitation ♪
That's right. The school cafeteria may be a refreshing experience.
That's right. It's always better than a bento.
I have a little question... Are you eating breakfast properly?
Hmmm, I eat well or not...
I wish I could, but shouldn't I go make it?
Hey you? I want to go to make breakfast again... how about?
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ If you like, please come and make it.
I want to make it ♪ Then I will go next time, so I promise.
For breakfast... I'll do my best myself.
That's right... Yeah, I understand. I'm supporting you as you work hard.
I've been crazy about making sweets lately. I want to feed you too, right?
really? I will gladly eat it!
Then I'll make it very delicious next time, so please look forward to it ▼
(What kind of sweets will come out?)
you know what? Also, I'd like to go to your house to make dinner... is that okay?
I don't mind that at all.
I'm glad ♪ Then I'll make it delicious, so please look forward to it ▼
I'm sorry... I wanted to do my best myself.
I see... sorry. But it's good to do your best on your own.
